 drivers/net/ppp/ppp_generic.c   | 13 +------------
 drivers/net/team/team.c         | 20 +-------------------
 include/linux/netdevice.h       | 19 +++++++++++++++++++
 net/bluetooth/6lowpan.c         | 14 +-------------
